  "text": "Found 6 Java source files in apache/flink's flink-streaming-java/src/ directory with @Deprecated annotations.\n\nCore DataStream API Deprecations (3 files):\n\n1. AscendingTimestampExtractor (flink-streaming-java/src/main/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/api/functions/timestamps/AscendingTimestampExtractor.java) - A timestamp assigner and watermark generator for streams with monotonously ascending timestamps. No explicit replacement is documented in the javadoc, but it implements WatermarkStrategyWithPeriodicWatermarks which may be the recommended approach.\n\n2. TextInputFormat (flink-streaming-java/src/main/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/api/legacy/io/TextInputFormat.java) - Input format that reads text files. Deprecated in favor of FLIP-27 FileSource and Sink-V2 FlinkSink. Recommendation from javadoc: \"If you want to read/write data from/to text file, please use FLIP-27 FileSource and Sink-V2 FlinkSink. This class should be removed if we drop the supports for read/write via input/output format in DataStream api.\"\n\n3. TextOutputFormat (flink-streaming-java/src/main/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/api/legacy/io/TextOutputFormat.java) - A FileOutputFormat that writes objects to text files. Deprecated in favor of FLIP-27 FileSource and Sink-V2 FlinkSink. Recommendation from javadoc: \"If you want to read/write data from/to text file, please use FLIP-27 FileSource and Sink-V2 FlinkSink. This class should be removed if we drop all supports for InputFormat and OutputFormat\"\n\nTest Infrastructure Deprecations (3 files):\n\n4. OneInputStreamTaskTestHarness (flink-streaming-java/src/test/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/runtime/tasks/OneInputStreamTaskTestHarness.java) - Test harness for testing OneInputStreamTask. Deprecated in favor of StreamTaskMailboxTestHarness and StreamTaskMailboxTestHarnessBuilder.\n\n5. StreamTaskTestHarness (flink-streaming-java/src/test/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/runtime/tasks/StreamTaskTestHarness.java) - Base test harness for testing StreamTask. Deprecated in favor of StreamTaskMailboxTestHarness and StreamTaskMailboxTestHarnessBuilder.\n\n6. TwoInputStreamTaskTestHarness (flink-streaming-java/src/test/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/runtime/tasks/TwoInputStreamTaskTestHarness.java) - Test harness for testing TwoInputStreamTask. Deprecated in favor of StreamTaskMailboxTestHarness and StreamTaskMailboxTestHarnessBuilder.\n\nThe main focus areas include:\n- Timestamp Extractors: AscendingTimestampExtractor (for handling monotonously ascending timestamps)\n- I/O Format Classes: TextInputFormat and TextOutputFormat (located in legacy/io package, recommending migration to newer FLIP-27 FileSource/Sink-V2 APIs)\n\nNo deprecated source functions or sink functions with @Deprecated annotations were found in the flink-streaming-java/src/ directory, though the legacy module contains deprecated I/O format classes that were used for reading/writing data."
}

